        <p>You can start vitamin supplements anytime after two weeks following surgery. They include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li> Biotin 10000 mcg tab, once daily </li>
            <li>Zinctron or Octozinc capsule, once daily</li>
            <li>Hemacaps or Feroglobin capsule, once daily</li>
            <li>Verdex ampoule, Â½ an ampoule on scalp every 3 days (to be applied for 20 minutes ");
                WriteLiteral(@"then hair is washed)</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Can I use workout related formulated protein supplements?</h3>
        <p>It is preferable to use the protein supplements prescribed by our team.</p>
        <h3>Is there an alternative for the monthly Vit B12 injection (Neurobion ampoule) in a different form?</h3>
        <p>Neurobion tablets can be used instead; one tablet every other day.</p>
